<head1>(Overview of Clock\overview)
<p>
 The DECwindows Clock displays the date, a digital 
 clock, and an analog clock. 
<p>
You can also set an
 alarm that displays a message on your screen and
 display time using 12- or 24-hour digital time.
<p>
Clock has three menus:  File, Options, and Help. Each menu 
contains menu items that you can choose.
<p>
For more information about using Clock, double
click on an item from the list of additional 
topics below.                      
<p>
For information about using help, choose Using Help from the 
Help menu above.

<P>
